v1.0.4 - new content + base layouts!

New Content:
+ New Crate - Space Crate (5 items)
+ New Crate - Candy Crate (6 items)
+ New Secret (hidden in one of the two new crates!)

+ New Rebirth (Life 4)
+ New Upgrades for Plot Size, Luck Multiplier, and Shiny Chance
+ Added a dropper for the ore processed 'Ore Processor' achievement.
+ Added an upgrader for unboxing 'Box Breaker' achievement
+ Added an upgrader for daily login 'Regular' achievement.

+ Base Layouts! You can now save layouts and share them with your friends!

New Setting:
+ Advanced Stats - See additional stats that couldn't originally fit on screen

Bug Fixes:
+ Fixed daily login 'Regular' achievement
+ Silenced HelpfulTips warnings (will be used in a future update)
+ Added a comma to ore value tooltip
- Removed the 'Ore Value Too High' notification. Will be added in a future update


Balance Changes:
+ Furnace Loot Secret item chance increased from 1/1M -> 1/100K
+ Money cap increased to 1Sp (from 50Qn)

New Changes:
+ Fixed some localization issues that made some icons not appear

+ Periastron's Throne now has stats
- Azure Scanner now actually scans, as it should have. The original static beam was not intended

DELAYED:
+ Inventory revamp, moving away from the bottom bar and rather a menu that pops up as needed.
+ Box Select, select many different items all at once!
+ Decorations can now be acquired through furnace loot
+ Remove Mode, so you can quickly remove items by just clicking on them
